      <LongDescription>The &lt;noparse&gt;CM-S-400 DF-21D&lt;/noparse&gt; is a size 4 waypoint-capable cruise missile.  It is based on the CM-S-4 body, which is a heavy support torpedo.  This missile will deliver no payload.  It homes in on its target using an Active Radar seeker  If the primary seeker does not find a target or is jammed, it can fall back on a Passive Wake seeker or a Radar Home-on-Jam seeker.

